Name: Lunarum Bracelet
AttributesDescription: A bracelet given to you by Iuno.
BgDescription: This bracelet has been with Iuno ever since she became a Priestess. Forged from lunarum and adorned with sprout motifs, it is not only a keepsake, but a quiet witness to her journey. Now, she entrusts it to you as a medium of Anchoring so you may draw upon her strength to reveal the Dark Tide creations.
ObtainedShowDescription: A bracelet given to you by Iuno, like a crescent moon resting on the wrist.
